[{"text": "Hang on because we're about", "start": 0.0, "duration": 4.537}, {"text": " to screech to a halt.", "start": 4.537, "duration": 2.603}, {"text": "That's right. ", "start": 7.14, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "The Earth is going to stop spinning ", "start": 8.074, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "for five seconds. ", "start": 10.71, "duration": 2.936}, {"text": "The Earth makes one full rotation", "start": 38.705, "duration": 2.769}, {"text": "on its axis in one day.", "start": 41.474, "duration": 2.503}, {"text": "This gives us day and night.", "start": 43.977, "duration": 3.47}, {"text": "The Earth is spinning ", "start": 47.447, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "because of collisions that happened", "start": 48.681, "duration": 2.236}, {"text": "when the planet was forming ", "start": 50.917, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "4.6 billion years ago.", "start": 53.053, "duration": 3.336}, {"text": "As a huge disk of gas and dust swirled", "start": 56.389, "duration": 3.704}, {"text": "around the Sun,", "start": 60.093, "duration": 1.201}, {"text": "dust and rock grains clumped together,", "start": 61.294, "duration": 3.036}, {"text": "generating forces ", "start": 64.33, "duration": 1.435}, {"text": "that kept the planet ", "start": 65.765, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "rotating in one direction.", "start": 67.133, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "You could imagine it ", "start": 69.936, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "much like a figure skater ", "start": 71.304, "duration": 1.635}, {"text": "spinning faster and faster. ", "start": 72.939, "duration": 2.436}, {"text": "And with almost no forces in space", "start": 75.375, "duration": 3.303}, {"text": "to slow the planet down,", "start": 78.678, "duration": 2.169}, {"text": "we keep rotating.", "start": 80.847, "duration": 1.935}, {"text": "And will continue ", "start": 82.782, "duration": 1.302}, {"text": "to for billions of years. ", "start": 84.084, "duration": 2.869}, {"text": "But if the Earth stopped on a dime,", "start": 86.953, "duration": 3.704}, {"text": "would you fly right off the surface?", "start": 90.657, "duration": 3.603}, {"text": "If the planet came to an abrupt halt,", "start": 94.26, "duration": 3.137}, {"text": "the atmosphere would still be in motion.", "start": 97.397, "duration": 3.603}, {"text": "That means though everything has lurched", "start": 101.0, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "to a stop,", "start": 103.736, "duration": 1.302}, {"text": "powerful winds would continue to blow.", "start": 105.038, "duration": 3.637}, {"text": "And this wouldn't be a strong breeze.", "start": 108.675, "duration": 3.637}, {"text": "They would be many times ", "start": 112.312, "duration": 1.668}, {"text": "stronger than any storm ", "start": 113.98, "duration": 1.902}, {"text": "you've ever encountered. ", "start": 115.882, "duration": 1.969}, {"text": "But the strength of these winds", "start": 117.851, "duration": 2.068}, {"text": "would differ ", "start": 119.919, "duration": 0.868}, {"text": "based on where you were on the planet.", "start": 120.787, "duration": 3.303}, {"text": "At or near the equator, ", "start": 124.09, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "the Earth is rotating the fastest. ", "start": 126.226, "duration": 3.036}, {"text": "Here you'd experience ", "start": 129.262, "duration": 1.501}, {"text": "wind speeds of 1,670 km/h (1,037 mph).", "start": 130.763, "duration": 4.839}, {"text": "Those winds would knock ", "start": 135.602, "duration": 1.668}, {"text": "you off your feet.", "start": 137.27, "duration": 1.535}, {"text": "But forget about you.", "start": 138.805, "duration": 2.235}, {"text": "These winds ", "start": 141.04, "duration": 1.102}, {"text": "would be strong enough ", "start": 142.142, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "to tear up the Earth's crust.", "start": 143.309, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "So it wouldn't matter ", "start": 146.045, "duration": 1.769}, {"text": "if you were out in an open field ", "start": 147.814, "duration": 1.902}, {"text": "or inside a steel-reinforced building.", "start": 149.716, "duration": 3.303}, {"text": "These winds would obliterate you.", "start": 153.019, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "For context, ", "start": 155.822, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "the strongest F5 tornadoes", "start": 156.956, "duration": 2.603}, {"text": "have velocities up ", "start": 159.559, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "to 511 km/h (318 mph).", "start": 160.793, "duration": 3.537}, {"text": "These storms can move houses", "start": 164.33, "duration": 2.536}, {"text": "off their foundations, ", "start": 166.866, "duration": 1.635}, {"text": "send cars flying ", "start": 168.501, "duration": 1.301}, {"text": "and even tear apart ", "start": 169.802, "duration": 1.502}, {"text": "concrete structures. ", "start": 171.304, "duration": 2.035}, {"text": "The winds from the Earth's ", "start": 173.339, "duration": 1.569}, {"text": "emergency brake ", "start": 174.908, "duration": 1.434}, {"text": "would be three times stronger than that.", "start": 176.342, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "So if the crust under your feet", "start": 179.145, "duration": 2.536}, {"text": "didn't crumble, ", "start": 181.681, "duration": 1.401}, {"text": "you and a lot of other stuff would likely", "start": 183.082, "duration": 2.87}, {"text": "go flying a great distance.", "start": 185.952, "duration": 3.27}, {"text": "But not off the face of the Earth.", "start": 189.222, "duration": 4.271}, {"text": "The escape velocity, ", "start": 193.493, "duration": 2.402}, {"text": "or the speed ", "start": 195.895, "duration": 0.634}, {"text": "you need to escape the Earth's", "start": 196.529, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "gravitational forces and enter space,", "start": 198.665, "duration": 3.003}, {"text": "is about 40,000 km/h (25,000 mph).", "start": 201.668, "duration": 3.603}, {"text": "In other parts of the world, ", "start": 205.271, "duration": 1.702}, {"text": "like New Zealand ", "start": 206.973, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": "or France, ", "start": 208.241, "duration": 1.068}, {"text": "you'd experience slightly weaker winds.", "start": 209.309, "duration": 3.169}, {"text": "But at 1,180 km/h (733 mph),", "start": 212.478, "duration": 3.804}, {"text": "these would still be much stronger", "start": 216.282, "duration": 2.469}, {"text": "than any storm ever. ", "start": 218.751, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "These winds ", "start": 220.82, "duration": 0.901}, {"text": "would pretty much destroy everything.", "start": 221.721, "duration": 3.737}, {"text": "But they wouldn't be ", "start": 225.458, "duration": 1.535}, {"text": "the only hazard ", "start": 226.993, "duration": 1.435}, {"text": "you'd need to keep an eye out ", "start": 228.428, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": "for in these short five seconds.", "start": 229.696, "duration": 3.136}, {"text": "Our planet is not a perfect sphere.", "start": 232.832, "duration": 3.637}, {"text": "It bulges near the equator", "start": 236.469, "duration": 2.035}, {"text": "due to the centrifugal forces ", "start": 238.504, "duration": 1.869}, {"text": "generated by the planet's rotation.", "start": 240.373, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "If the rotation stopped,", "start": 243.109, "duration": 2.102}, {"text": "the Earth would transform", "start": 245.211, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "quickly into a perfect sphere.", "start": 247.28, "duration": 3.203}, {"text": "All the water gathering near ", "start": 250.483, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "the equator would flow away", "start": 252.552, "duration": 2.536}, {"text": "toward the poles,", "start": 255.088, "duration": 1.468}, {"text": "generating a massive tsunami.", "start": 256.556, "duration": 3.37}, {"text": "Five seconds later, ", "start": 259.926, "duration": 1.535}, {"text": "when the planet returned", "start": 261.461, "duration": 2.002}, {"text": "to its full-speed rotation, ", "start": 263.463, "duration": 2.169}, {"text": "that water would backtrack.", "start": 265.632, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "A wall of water ", "start": 268.368, "duration": 1.534}, {"text": "would slam into everything", "start": 269.902, "duration": 2.136}, {"text": "and everyone.", "start": 272.038, "duration": 1.635}, {"text": "Twice.", "start": 273.673, "duration": 1.468}, {"text": "That's one heck of a storm. ", "start": 275.141, "duration": 2.669}, {"text": "Maybe the only place you'd be safe", "start": 277.81, "duration": 2.803}, {"text": "in this scenario", "start": 280.613, "duration": 1.268}, {"text": " is near the North or South Poles.", "start": 281.881, "duration": 3.704}, {"text": "Here, the wind would be the mildest. ", "start": 285.585, "duration": 3.97}, {"text": "You must be relieved to hear", "start": 289.555, "duration": 2.069}, {"text": "that the Earth has returned ", "start": 291.624, "duration": 1.769}, {"text": "to its normal rotation after all this.", "start": 293.393, "duration": 2.202}, {"text": "But like I said, ", "start": 295.595, "duration": 1.368}, {"text": "there would be nothing left on it.", "start": 296.963, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "Every building, all farmland", "start": 299.599, "duration": 3.003}, {"text": "and all technology ", "start": 302.602, "duration": 1.401}, {"text": "would be demolished beyond recognition.", "start": 304.003, "duration": 3.404}, {"text": "Billions of people, ", "start": 307.407, "duration": 1.534}, {"text": "if not every single person on Earth,", "start": 308.941, "duration": 2.97}, {"text": "would die from the brute force", "start": 311.911, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "of being slammed", "start": 314.547, "duration": 1.401}, {"text": " by the massive gusts of wind. ", "start": 315.948, "duration": 2.436}, {"text": "So if you're looking to survive", "start": 318.384, "duration": 2.736}, {"text": "this apocalyptic scenario,", "start": 321.12, "duration": 2.636}, {"text": "you'd better start ", "start": 323.756, "duration": 1.702}, {"text": "building an underground bunker.", "start": 325.458, "duration": 3.036}, {"text": "Luckily, it's expected the Earth ", "start": 328.494, "duration": 2.87}, {"text": "won't come to a halt ", "start": 331.364, "duration": 1.635}, {"text": "any time in the next few billion years.", "start": 332.999, "duration": 3.804}, {"text": "And before that, ", "start": 336.803, "duration": 1.201}, {"text": "the Sun would burn out ", "start": 338.004, "duration": 1.668}, {"text": "and turn into a red giant.", "start": 339.672, "duration": 3.437}, {"text": "But that's a story for another WHAT IF.", "start": 343.109, "duration": 5.138}]